                <li style=""margin-left:20px;""><i class=""icon-ok""></i>What are the objectives of the website & what problem does it solve?</li>
                <li style=""margin-left:20px;""><i class=""icon-ok""></i>Who");
            WriteLiteral(@" will be the target users of the website?</li>
                <li style=""margin-left:20px;""><i class=""icon-ok""></i>The intended benefit that the users would get when they visit your website.</li>
                <li style=""margin-left:20px;""><i class=""icon-ok""></i>The primary aim of the website such as informing, selling, getting the users to sign up for a service, or anything else.</li>
                <li style=""margin-left:20px;""><i class=""icon-ok""></i>The strengths and the weaknesses of a competitor website that operates within the same niche you are planning to launch.</li>

                <li style=""margin-left:20px;""><i class=""icon-cloud-download""></i><span style=""font-size: 16px!important; font-weight:bold!important;"">Strategy Planning</span></li>
