                <li style=""margin-left:20px;""><i class=""icon-ok""></i>Content Strategy planning</li>

                <li style=""margin-left:20px;""><i class=""icon-cloud-download""></i><span style=""font-size: 16px!important; font-weight:bold!important;"">Design and development</span></li>
                At this stage, we incorporate the design elements of the website according to the existing brand elements such as logo design, the colour scheme, etc. followed by the actual coding process. Both front-end and back-end development need to be focused during the development phase.</li>
                <br />
                <br />
                <li style=""margin-left:20px;""><i class=""icon-cloud-download""></i><span style=""font-size: 16px!important; font-weight:bold!important;"">Testing of the website</span></li>
                Testing of the website is a crit");
